high_descs: Go to the toilet tank and pick up the spraybottle.
Take the desklamp to the nightstand to clean.
anns.task_desc: Getting the SprayBottle to clean the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn your left and walk into the bathroom and then turn to your left and reach the spray bottle which is on the toilet seat.
Take the spraybottle from top of the toilet seat.
Turn towards your right, take a walk and once again turn towards your right and then enter into your bedroom and take a right turn and reach the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the SprayBottle by the light of a DeskLamp.

high_descs: TURN TWO LEFT TO REACH TOILET FASHION
TAKE SPRAY BOTTLE FROM TOILET FASHION
TURN 3 RIGHT TO REACH DESK LAMP
SWITCH ON DESK LAMP USING SPRAY BOTTLE
anns.task_desc: TO SWITCH ON DESK LAMP USING SPRAY BOTTLE
